Package: EstimatingBiologicalVariation
Type: Package
Title: Estimating Biological Variation with Bayesian Models
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Pernille", "Fauskanger", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "pernille.fauskanger@noklus.no")
Description: A Shiny application for estimating biological variation
    components (analytical, within-individual, and between-individual)
    using Bayesian hierarchical models fitted via Stan. Includes
    interactive data exploration, prior elicitation, MCMC diagnostics,
    and rich D3-based visualisations. Ships with Rcpp routines for fast
    variance-component estimation (ANOVA and bootstrap CIs) and Stan data
    preparation.
